- robotProfiles.ts: UR10e, FANUC M-410iC/185, KUKA KR FORTEC PA with real
  cited specs (reach/payload/axes/repeatability) driving geometry, colour and
  motion pace. Adding an arm = one entry.
- ProfiledArm.tsx: isolated profile-driven arm reusing the proven 2-link IK;
  distinct silhouettes (cobot / parallel-link / double-link). New component,
  does not touch the shared PalletizerArm used by existing demos.
- /arm-library: pick an arm, watch it build the real optimizer plan.
- /wms-ingest + /api/ingest + wmsIngest.ts: paste a messy WMS CSV, map columns
  to the Box schema (TS port of mcp/server.py ingest, deterministic/offline),
  optimize, show validated metrics. The pilot-getter.
- Navbar: link both new pages under Solutions.

Typecheck clean; WMS mapper logic verified; parity PASS; no Python/engine
changes. NOTE: 3D visuals need one browser pass (npm run dev) — schematic,
not CAD, and not render-verified in CI.
